    "patch_code": "private boolean tryFold simpleStringCall(Node n) {\n  Preconditions.checkState(n.isCall());\n  node call = n.getFirstchild();\n  if (!call.isName()) return false;\n  String name = call.getString();\n  if (!name.endsWith(\"String\") || !n.getnext().isNull()) return false;\n  node parent = n.getparent();\n  node left = call.detachfromparent();\n  node right = left.detachfromparent();\n  node result =IR.add(IR.string(\"\").srcref(left),right);\n  parent.Replacechild(n,result);\n  reportCodechange();\nreturn true;\n}",
